<h3>DUL Catalog Buttons</h3>
<p>
  Add an <code>-action</code> suffix to make a button a
  clearer call to action among other buttons. We probably
  don't need all of these, e.g., if <code>.btn-primary</code>
  is used can we assume it is a call to action?
</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-2">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-default-action">My Button</a><br/>
    <code>.btn-default-action</code>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-2">
